    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>萍城异闻录 DEMO</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是萍城异闻录的demo版本，在这个版本中，您可以体验游戏的大部分功能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >萍城异闻录，PC端正式开测，加入玩家群向我们反馈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前已开放官方玩家群，群内会同步更新一手情报，举办内测及其他福利活动，还有机会参加赛事赢取京东卡等实物奖励，欢迎各位少侠加入一起参与讨论！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方玩家01群：342072404</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/dcbeaed0abb54e75bba4b2f74a148af1.poster.avif?t=1767665509\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/dcbeaed0abb54e75bba4b2f74a148af1.webm?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/dcbeaed0abb54e75bba4b2f74a148af1.mp4?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款让人耳目一新的吃鸡游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单局中商店可随机刷新助战英雄，玩家通过击杀怪物获得金币，购买助战英雄以获得英雄之力，几十种不同的阵容搭配，带给玩家惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8种元素同台竞技，相互元素融合，组合成多元化的伤害效果，值得发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >羁绊系统，深化阵容搭配重要性。专属的助战英雄，触发强力的羁绊效果，产生多重打击特效，创意成就感强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >躲猫猫，变身系统可躲避追踪，暗算敌对玩家，并增加趣味性操作空间，战斗过程其乐无穷。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【助战连携羁绊】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，随时可以招募助战角色，与你的主战角色形成搭配，触发超强合体技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄之间，互有羁绊效果，组建适合的阵容，触发羁绊效果，使战斗更有深度和养成性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9f6572f59e560b2572afd12ada57df0a.poster.avif?t=1767665509\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9f6572f59e560b2572afd12ada57df0a.webm?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9f6572f59e560b2572afd12ada57df0a.mp4?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【躲猫猫】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >添加了躲猫猫系统，你可以在场景内，变成各式各样的形态，以躲避其他玩家的追踪，或者暗算其他玩家，又或者为自己提供一个安全的环境，来查询助战英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/aff1210fdea276c262eba55908531d91.poster.avif?t=1767665509\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/aff1210fdea276c262eba55908531d91.webm?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/aff1210fdea276c262eba55908531d91.mp4?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【元素反应】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有8种元素伤害，除了物理以外的7种元素 互相均能产生元素反应，不同德元素反应，为目标带来的负面效果均不同，这也影响到了你的阵容选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9dd24acd30f84c8558d7a51cf5b3679d.poster.avif?t=1767665509\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9dd24acd30f84c8558d7a51cf5b3679d.webm?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9dd24acd30f84c8558d7a51cf5b3679d.mp4?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【大魔王】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中，你可以通过击败场景中的龙兽，获得龙魂，龙魂会让你化身为大魔王，伤害变高，但同时也会让你受到更高的伤害，此时你会变成场上最显眼的那一个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/2d4940694c445868d9e4f3fc5133d055.poster.avif?t=1767665509\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/2d4940694c445868d9e4f3fc5133d055.webm?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/2d4940694c445868d9e4f3fc5133d055.mp4?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【闪避、格挡、浮空追击、轻功】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗包含了多样化的行为方式，灵活的使用他们，成为战斗大师吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9aff1d519f3b60d571435f871433bc07.poster.avif?t=1767665509\" width=612 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9aff1d519f3b60d571435f871433bc07.webm?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185930/extras/9aff1d519f3b60d571435f871433bc07.mp4?t=1767665509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【丰富的PVE内容】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >已完成了大量的PVE内容，将在未来与大家见面。</p>",
